-- Citigroup says to launch Nikko bid on March 15
-- 
-- Wed Mar 14, 2007 5:52am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/03/14/us-nikko-citi-tender-idUSTKV00322120070314

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Citigroup ( C.N ) said its planned tender offer for Japanese brokerage Nikko Cordial 8603.T would start on Thursday and run through to April 26. 


 Citigroup reiterated its offer to buy Nikko's shares at 1,700 yen apiece. Citigroup had sweetened its takeover bid for the brokerage from 1,350 yen on Tuesday.